&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&gt;** Dinobot growled as Tavatron approached him and the small ball of fur on 
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&gt;his nose, knowing that she was trying to help him but not quite wanting 
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&gt;anyone near him at the moment. Glaring at the fembot as he stood there and 
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&gt;watched her hand come closer and closer to the black ball of lint. 
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&gt;For some unexplainable reason Tavatron&#39;s sudden apology heightened his 
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&gt;aggression and his eyes turned into slits. This was pathetic! Since when had 
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&gt;he needed the help of others in a foolish situation such as this? It 
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&gt;was...absurd! A grown man such as himself with a history of bloodshed, 
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&gt;seeming helpless just because a black ball from Hell landed on his snout! 
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&gt;What foolishness! However, Dinobot remained where he was as Tavatron 
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&gt;leaned close and the small creature decided to use her nose as a target, the 
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&gt;female jumping back and whimpering quietly in alarm. 
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&gt;Dinobot only snarled and rolled his eyes, getting sick of the little game, 
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&gt;which this creature was deciding to play with the both of them. Thinking and 
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&gt;wondering if it had any clue that it would be nothing but stray whips of 
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&gt;fuzz on the wind if he ever got his transmetal claws on it. It was already 
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&gt;stamped DEAD as far as he was concerned. Dinobot jerked his head towards 
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&gt;Tavatron as she tore her staff from sub-space, wondering if she was going to 
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&gt;take some sort of revenge upon the ball-o-fuzz resting comfortably upon his 
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&gt;most highly reflective snout. However, was not eager to see if his thoughts 
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&gt;were false...or her aim. There was one fact, which Tavatron would have to 
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&gt;catch up upon before she so much of moved a metallic muscle, and that was 
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&gt;that if she hit him instead of the cat she would have a pair of transmetal 
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&gt;fangs to try and pry off of her throat. She was indeed his friend, yes...but 
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&gt;no bot hit him and got away with it. 
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&gt;Dinobot snarled in response to her telling of him to remain still, shaking 
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&gt;his head to try and rid himself of the creature before moving it down and 
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&gt;reaching towards it with his own claws. If it tried to swat him, he would 
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&gt;simply squish it, then peel it off of his snout. Which suited him just as 
&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;&gt;well.** 
